Class StartEndCommand

  • java.lang.Object
    • edu.wpi.first.wpilibj.frc2.command.SendableCommandBase

  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Command, edu.wpi.first.wpilibj.Sendable
    public class StartEndCommand
extends SendableCommandBase
    A command that runs a given runnable when it is initalized, and another runnable when it ends. Useful for running and then stopping a motor, or extending and then retracting a solenoid. Has no end condition as-is; either subclass it or use Command.withTimeout(double) or Command.interruptOn(BooleanSupplier) to give it one.
